　國　  111   年  　7     月　　27    日\r\n                              書  記  官  黃柏睿","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/NHEM/111%2c%e6%b9%96%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c213%2c20221019%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"NHEM,111,湖交簡,213,20221019,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"湖交簡","JNO":"213","JDATE":"20221019","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}